Class ArtifactAdditionalInfoDto

  • java.lang.Object

    ReadOnlyAdditionalInfoDto

    public class ArtifactAdditionalInfoDto
extends IdentifiableDto
    Additional editing information attached to an artifact. All editing/approval settings only apply to the artifact head revision.
